{"tid":2258440,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「6GB ram」12 pro超強大！保留後台背景app防reload能力遠超「4GB ram」","createTime":"2020-10-26T04:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T15:35:59.000Z","uid":109923,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"54376c82f1cacf9bfadad01480c18ef39ee7152f","tid":2258440,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUhu2t5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUhu2t5.png&h=c9dc39cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 2nd lap 12 pro完全冇reload，28秒完成<br />\n11pro同Xs分別用咗1:30同1:17<br />\n<br />\n從上至下，11pro同Xs都係去到among us已經reload咗<br />\n相信更新多兩代iOS個差距會越嚟越明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8whSfO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8whSfO4.png&h=647cd82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好鬧iPhone12系列嘅電量唧牙膏啦，因為iPhone11系列嘅RAM擠咗牙膏，所以加電量<br />\nApple都識玩intel 嗰套 tick tock model<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Apple 係 tick(電量) tock(RAM)  tick tock  tick tock 咁上，加電唔加RAM，加RAM就唔加電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回顧 unwire 班傻閪豬隊友：「4GB ram夠用啦，30~40 apps喺背景備用緊呀，12pro俾你6GB係為咗賺更多，ram多咗跑分唔會勁咗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\niOS由「1GB ram夠用」進化到「2GB夠用」，今年變「4GB夠用」「12pro 6GB係昆錢」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2248888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2248888</a>"},{"pid":"d056ffa4192e331d0e851ce7b6fa113d204b0391","tid":2258440,"uid":38556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"想睇12 pro同12分別"},{"pid":"0ddb5eb17fd176f3c7ba6fe0995c5fc0c5624ac9","tid":2258440,"uid":255557,"like":8,"dislike":24,"score":-16,"citedBy"